wiiremotej
Class GuitarCalibrationData

java.lang.Object
  wiiremotej.GuitarCalibrationData

public class GuitarCalibrationData
extends java.lang.Object

Contains calibration data for use in WRGuitarExtensionEvents. Immutable. Be aware that if buttons are held when the controller is first connected (or the remote is turned on while the controller is plugged in), calibration data may be inaccurate.

whammyBarMax

public double whammyBarMax()
Returns whammyBarMax. whammyBarMax is the maximum value for the whammyBar WITHOUT zero adjustment. Actual max is whammyBarMax-whammyBarZero. Always is 31.
